igcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20seen%20those%20mistakes%20up%20close.%20Well-meaning%20efforts%20once%20led%20to%20planting%20non-native%20trees%20that%20upset%20the%20natural%20balance.%20When%20the%20National%20Park%20was%20declared%2C%20fences%20went%20up%2C%20cutting%20people%20off%20from%20the%20resources%20they%20had%20always%20relied%20on%20%E2%80%94%20honey%2C%20crabs%2C%20medicinal%20plants%2C%20even%20mangrove%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHalf-knowledge%20is%20worse%20than%20no%20knowledge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20firmly.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20protect%20an%20ecosystem%20by%20shutting%20out%20the%20people%20who%20understand%20it%20best.%20When%20livelihoods%20vanish%2C%20people%20migrate%2C%20land%20lies%20abandoned%2C%20and%20the%20bond%20between%20community%20and%20forest%20begins%20to%20fray.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPutting%20people%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20climate%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20belief%20in%20local%20wisdom%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Socratus%20Foundation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20began%20working%20in%20Odisha%20in%202020.%20Their%20idea%20is%20simple%3A%20complex%20problems%20need%20solutions%20built%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20%E2%80%94%20and%20from%20those%20living%20with%20these%20realities%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20foundation%2C%20voices%20like%20Nirakar%E2%80%99s%20and%20Madhusmit%E2%80%99s%20must%20lead%20the%20conversation%20on%20climate%20action.%20Strategies%20borrowed%20from%20the%20West%20and%20applied%20to%20small%20Indian%20villages%2C%20they%20say%2C%20rarely%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Socratus%20creates%20spaces%20where%20science%20meets%20lived%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20in%20words%20people%20use%20every%20day.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20conversations%20dri