%20reviving%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20clear%3A%20help%20people%20move%20from%20feeling%20powerless%20to%20feeling%20capable%20and%20in%20control.%20To%20make%20this%20vision%20real%2C%20Socratus%20created%20a%20coalition%20of%20civil%20society%20organisations%20active%20in%20India%20and%20Odisha.%20Their%20collaborators%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bakul%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20volunteer-driven%20movement%20in%20Odisha%20enabling%20public%20initiatives%20like%20free%20libraries%20and%20art%20programmes.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESambad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20major%20Odia%20news%20outlet.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoonj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20humanitarian%20organisation%20working%20on%20disaster%20relief%20and%20rural%20development.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESELCO%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy-based%20solutions.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Socratus%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20test%20its%20ideas%2C%20Odisha%20felt%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20The%20state%20lives%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20cyclones%20and%20floods.%20Its%20landscapes%20%E2%80%94%20from%20dense%20forests%20to%20fragile%20coastlines%20%E2%80%94%20are%20among%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20also%20had%20a%20strong%20base%20to%20build%20on.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20adopt%20a%20comprehensive%20climate%20action%20plan%2C%20with%20systems%20stretching%20from%20the%20grassroots%20to%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20are%20the%20people.%20Nearly%2023%20percent%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%2064%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Twelve%20out%20of%20its%2030%20districts%20are%20tribal-dominated%2C%20home%20to%20communities%20living%20across%20forests%2C%20wetlands%2C%20farmlands%2C%20and%20coastal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20its%20philosophy%20to%20life%2C%20Socratus%20teamed%20up%20with%20organisations%20like%20Sambad%20and%20Bakul%20Foundation%20and%20launched%20the%20Climate%20Panchayat%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20colourful%20maps%20of%20Odisha%20showing%20groundwater%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20trends.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-175x300.jpg%20175w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-768x1314.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-898x1536.jpg%20898w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-150x257.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935.jpg%20988w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478542%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sessions%20bring%20together%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20a%20locality%20%E2%80%94%20men%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20forest%20workers%2C%20youth%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20even%20MLAs%20sometimes%2C%E2