n%5C%22%3EClimate%20Panchayats%20unite%20villagers%2C%20experts%2C%20and%20officials%20to%20co-create%20solutions%20for%20climate%20resilience.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20are%20also%20bringing%20back%20traditional%20varieties%20of%20aromatic%20rice%20%E2%80%94%20Leelavati%2C%20Basuabhoga%2C%20and%20Haladigundi.%20These%20grains%20are%20more%20than%20food%3B%20they%20are%20organic%2C%20resilient%2C%20and%20rooted%20in%20local%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20ideas%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20the%20fields.%20From%20these%20conversations%20have%20come%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20Socratus%2C%20along%20with%20SELCO%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club%2C%20is%20working%20to%20install%20solar-powered%20food%20processors%20and%20set%20up%20new%20livelihood%20options%20like%20puffed%20rice%20units%2C%20mushroom%20cultivation%20centres%2C%20and%20agarbatti-making%20setups.%20A%20prototype%20is%20even%20in%20the%20works%20to%20replace%20diesel%20and%20petrol%20boats%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20National%20Park%20with%20solar-powered%20ones.%20All%20of%20this%20began%20with%20people%20sitting%20together%20and%20sharing%20their%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reminder%20that%20when%20communities%20lead%2C%20solutions%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20help%20others%20turn%20their%20lives%20around%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20driving%20this%20change%20are%20120%20local%20women%20trained%20by%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club%20as%20Climate%20Champions%20under%20the%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20ECRICC%20(Enhancing%20Climate%20Resilience%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Coastal%20Communities)%20project.%20They%20spread%20awareness%2C%20share%20practical%20knowledge%2C%20and%20have%20become%20trusted%20voices%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20is%20Sabita%20Behera%2C%20whose%20life%20reflects%20both%20the%20struggles%20and%20strength%20of%20Bhitarkanika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabita%20was%20just%2012%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20mother.%20With%20an%20ailing%20father%20and%20a%20younger%20brother%20to%20care%20for%2C%20she%20often%20had%20to%20beg%20for%20money%20to%20cover%20hospital%20bills%20in%20Cuttack.%20She%20married%20young%20and%2C%20like%20many%20from%20Odisha%2C%20migrated%20with%20her%20husband%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20work%20as%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%20and%20repay%20debts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20COVID%20%E2%80%94%20and%20with%20it%2C%20even%20tougher%20days.%20Long%20hours%2C%20meagre%20wages%2C%20and%20caring%20for%20a%20toddler%20became%20impossible%20to%20manage%20together.%20Sabita%20returned%20to%20her%20village%20near%20Bhitarkanika%20with%20her%20child%20while%20her%20husband%20stayed%20back%20to%20earn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20farming%20a%20small%20rented%20plot%2C%20doing%20everything%20herself%20to%20save%20money%20%E2%80%94%20from%20transplanting%20saplings%20to%20harvesting%20crops.%20Over%20time%2C%20she%20learnt%20about%20the%20damage%20chemical%20farming%20was%20causing%20and%20switched%20completely%20to%20organic%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753884862.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sabita%20Behera%2C%20a%20farmer%20and%20Climate%20Champion%2C%20promotes%20organic%20farming%20and%20empowers%20women%20in%20Bhitarkanika.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753884862.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753884862-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753884862-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette