mpses%20of%20our%20AI%20systems%20improving%20themselves.%20The%20improvement%20is%20slow%20for%20now%2C%20but%20undeniable.%20Developing%20superintelligence%20is%20now%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20seems%20clear%20that%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20AI%20will%20improve%20all%20our%20existing%20systems%20and%20enable%20the%20creation%20and%20discovery%20of%20new%20things%20that%20aren't%20imaginable%20today.%20But%20it%20is%20an%20open%20question%20what%20we%20will%20direct%20superintelligence%20towards.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20some%20ways%20this%20will%20be%20a%20new%20era%20for%20humanity%2C%20but%20in%20others%20it's%20just%20a%20continuation%20of%20historical%20trends.%20As%20recently%20as%20200%20years%20ago%2C%2090%25%20of%20people%20were%20farmers%20growing%20food%20to%20survive.%20Advances%20in%20technology%20have%20steadily%20freed%20much%20of%20humanity%20to%20focus%20less%20on%20subsistence%20and%20more%20on%20the%20pursuits%20we%20choose.%20At%20each%20step%2C%20people%20have%20used%20our%20newfound%20productivity%20to%20achieve%20more%20than%20was%20previously%20possible%2C%20pushing%20the%20frontiers%20of%20science%20and%20health%2C%20as%20well%20as%20spending%20more%20time%20on%20creativity%2C%20culture%2C%20relationships%2C%20and%20enjoying%20life.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20am%20extremely%20optimistic%20that%20superintelligence%20will%20help%20humanity%20accelerate%20our%20pace%20of%20progress.%20But%20perhaps%20even%20more%20important%20is%20that%20superintelligence%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20begin%20a%20new%20era%20of%20personal%20empowerment%20where%20people%20will%20have%20greater%20agency%20to%20improve%20the%20world%20in%20the%20directions%20they%20choose.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20profound%20as%20the%20abundance%20produced%20by%20AI%20may%20one%20day%20be%2C%20an%20even%20more%20meaningful%20impact%20on%20our%20lives%20will%20likely%20come%20from%20everyone%20having%20a%20personal%20superintelligence%20that%20helps%20you%20achieve%20your%20goals%2C%20create%20what%20you%20want%20to%20see%20in%20the%20world%2C%20experience%20any%20adventure%2C%20be%20a%20better%20friend%20to%20those%20you%20care%20about%2C%20and%20grow%20to%20become%20the%20person%20you%20aspire%20to%20be.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMeta's%20vision%20is%20to%20bring%20personal%20superintelligence%20to%20everyone.%20We%20believe%20in%20putting%20this%20power%20in%20people's%20hands%20to%20direct%20it%20towards%20what%20they%20value%20in%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20distinct%20from%20others%20in%20the%20industry%20who%20believe%20superintelligence%20should%20be%20directed%20centrally%20towards%20automating%20all%20valuable%20work%2C%20and%20then%20humanity%20will%20live%20on%20a%20dole%20of%20its%20output.%20At%20Meta%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20people%20pursuing%20their%20individual%20aspirations%20is%20how%20we%20have%20always%20made%20progress%20expanding%20prosperity%2C%20science%2C%20health%2C%20and%20culture.%20This%20will%20be%20increasingly%20important%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20intersection%20of%20technology%20and%20how%20people%20live%20is%20Meta's%20focus%2C%20and%20this%20will%20only%20become%20more%20important%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20trends%20continue%2C%20then%20you'd%20expect%20people%20to%20spend%20less%20time%20in%20productivity%20software%2C%20and%20more%20time%20creating%20and%20connecting.%20Personal%20superintelligence%20that%20knows%20us%20deeply%2C%20understands%20our%20goals%2C%20and%20can%20help%20us%20achieve%20them%20will%20be%20by%20far%20the%20most%20useful.%20Personal%20devices%20like%20glasses%20that%20understand%20our%20context%20because%20they%20can%20see%20what%20we%20see%2C%20hear%20what%20we%20hear%2C%20and%20interact%20with%20us%20throughout%20the%20day%20will%20become%20our%20primary%20computing%20devices.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20believe%20the%20benefits%20of%20superintelligence%20should%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20world%20as%20broadly%20as%20possible.%20That%20said%2C%20superintelligence%20will%20raise%20novel%20safety%20concerns.%20We'll%20need%20to%20be%20rigorous%20about%20mitigating%20these%20risks%20and%20careful%20about%20what%20we%20choose%20to%20open%20source.%20Still%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20building%20a%20free%20society%20requires%20that%20we%20aim%20to%20empower%20people%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20rest%20of%20this%20decade%20seems%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20decisive%20period%20for%20determining%20the%20path%20this%20technology%20will%20take%2C%20and%20whether%20superintelligence%20will%20be%20a%20tool%20for%20personal%20empowerment%20or%20a%20force%20focused%20on%20replacing%20large%20swaths%20of%20society.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMeta%20believes%20strongly%20in%20building%20personal%20superintelligence%20that%20empowers%20everyone.%20We%20have%20the%20resources%20and%20the%20expertise%20to%20build%20the%20massive%20infrastructure%20required%2C%20and%20the%20capability%20and%20will%20to%20deliver%20new%20technology%20to%20billions%20of%20people%20across%20our%20products.%20I'm%20excited%20to%20focus%20Meta's%20efforts%20towards%20building%20this%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Mark%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-personal-superintelligence-ai-letter-meta-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753883926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d0d9ea466d2b74ab571db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-personal-superintelligence-ai-letter-meta-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20that