n%20edited%20or%20artificially%20generated.%20Other%20users%20then%20rate%20the%20submission's%20accuracy%20and%20helpfulness.%20If%20enough%20support%20it%2C%20it%20could%20get%20added%20below%20an%20offending%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20footnotes%20feature%20arrives%20at%20a%20key%20moment%20for%20TikTok%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-gets-news-from-tiktok-influencers-media-industry-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20news%20source%20for%20young%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20year%2C%2017%25%20of%20US%20adults%20said%20they%20regularly%20get%20news%20on%20the%20site%2C%20up%20from%203%25%20in%202020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20is%20not%20relying%20solely%20on%20footnotes%20to%20address%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20uses%20automation%20and%20human%20moderators%20to%20track%20down%20false%20content%2C%20working%20with%20a%20global%20network%20of%20fact-checkers%20to%20identify%20misinformation%20in%20different%20markets.%20But%20for%20app%20users%2C%20footnotes%20may%20quickly%20become%20one%20of%20the%20more%20visible%20forms%20of%20content%20review%20happening%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20posting%20footnotes%2C%20a%20user%20must%20be%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20have%20been%20on%20the%20app%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%2C%20and%20have%20no%20recent%20community%20violations%20on%20their%20record.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20had%20registered%20around%2080%2C000%20participants%20to%20seed%20the%20product%20at%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20that%20may%20crop%20up%20for%20TikTok%20is%20defining%20what%20is%20or%20isn't%20good%20information%20in%20a%20footnote%20(an%20area%20of%20contention%20in%20the%20US%20media%20landscape%20where%20political%20divisions%20run%20deep).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20submitting%20a%20footnote%2C%20TikTok%20asks%20users%20to%20provide%20a%20link%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Breliable%20source%26quot%3B%20to%20support%20their%20claim%2C%20though%20TikTok%20isn't%20dictating%20what%20is%20or%20isn't%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20we're%20letting%20our%20users%20choose%20which%20links%20to%20upload%20and%20after%20we%20go%20live%2C%20we'll%20be%20taking%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20sources%20that%20come%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Erica%20Ruzic%2C%20TikTok's%20global%20head%20of%20integrity%20and%20authenticity%20product%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20an%20event%20hosted%20at%20the%20company's%20New%20York%20offices.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20let%20our%20users%20decide%20what%20they're%20deeming%20an%20authoritative%20source%20to%20begin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20footnotes%20will%20only%20appear%20on%20the%20original%20offending%20video%2C%20which%20means%20duets%20or%20stitches%20won't%20get%20flagged.%20They%20also%20won't%20appear%20on%20content%20from%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20program%20may%20depend%20on%20TikTok's%20ability%20to%20prevent%20its%20system%20from%20being%20gamed%2C%20as%20bad%20actors%20might%20try%20to%20flood%20the%20zone%20with%20misinformation%20on%20a%20particular%20topic%2C%20Angie%20Drobnic%20Holan%2C%20director%20of%20the%20International%20Fact-Checking%20Network%2C%20said%20during%20a%20Tuesday%20panel%20at%20TikTok's%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speed%20at%20which%20a%20footnote%20is%20submitted%2C%20reviewed%2C%20and%20posted%20will%20also%20be%20an%20important%20factor%20in%20the%20program's%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20bad%20content%20that's%20harmful%20goes%20viral%2C%20it%20doesn't%20go%20viral%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20it%20goes%20viral%20in%20one%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberta%20Braga%2C%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Digital%20Democracy%20Institute%20of%20the%20Americas%2C%20said%20during%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-community-fact-checking-us-following-x-lead-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753873201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6889255e85e81483682ee221%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-community-fact-checking-us-following-x-lead-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TikTok%20is%20launching%20its%20own%20version%20of%20community%20notes%20in%20the%20US%20as%20looks%20to%20police%20bad%20or%20misleading%20videos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dwhateley%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-community-fact-checking-us-following-x-lead-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyundai%20Q1FY26%20result%3A%20Profit%20down%208%25%20at%20%E2%82%B91%2C369%20crore%2C%20revenue%20falls%205.5%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753873065000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fquarterly-results%2Fhyundai-motor-india-q1-fy26-result-profit-revenue-shares-earnings-dividend-125073000883_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hyundai%20Q1%20FY26%20result%3A%20The%20dip%20follows%20a%206.1%20per%20cent%20decline%20in%20sales%20to%20180%2C399%20units%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20from%20192%2C055%20units%20in%20Q1FY25%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fquarterly-results%2Fhyundai-motor-india-q1-fy26-result-profit-revenue-shares-earnings-dividend-125073000883_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20called%20'Devdas'%20BGM%20'bakwas'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753872946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.c