autiful%20rainbows%20during%20the%20spring.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Wildfire%20Partners%20representative%20came%20out%20that%20spring%2C%20he%20tagged%20over%2030%20trees%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20cut%20down.%20His%2017-page%20assessment%20also%20involved%20trimming%20ladder%20fuels%20and%20fireproofing%20our%20house's%20exterior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20and%20when%20we%20completed%20our%20wildfire%20mitigation%20checklist%2C%20Wildfire%20Partners%20would%20come%20back%2C%20verify%20the%20work%2C%20and%20issue%20a%20certification.%20They%20would%20also%20match%20up%20to%20%242%2C000%20of%20arborist-related%20costs%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20would%20be%20on%20us%20to%20fund.%20The%20proposed%20scope%20of%20work%20would%20cost%20upwards%20of%20%2450%2C000%2C%20or%20several%20thousand%20less%20if%20you%20were%20able%20to%20DIY%20some%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20assessor%20assured%20us%20that%20most%20people%20take%20years%20to%20complete%20their%20checklists%20due%20to%20the%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20effort%20required.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20debated%20our%20plan%20of%20approach%20and%20decided%20we%20would%20sleep%20better%20at%20night%20knowing%20we%20had%20taken%20all%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-wildfires-fireproof-my-home-roofs-siding-building-code-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotect%20our%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e16a6aab-1d3d-42b5-823c-5edb7df11f64%5C%22%3EA%20grassland%20fire%20put%20us%20on%20edge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20with%20dog%20in%20colorado%20wilderness%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e593f748d8c055f668eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore%20with%20their%20dog%20in%20their%20backyard%20with%20beautiful%20mountain%20views.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20first%20(and%20only)%20summer%20in%20our%20dream%20home%2C%20we%20spent%20weekends%20working%20toward%20our%20certification.%20We%20felled%20dozens%20of%20trees%2C%20stacked%20logs%2C%20and%20gave%20them%20away.%20Friends%20pitched%20in%2C%20and%20a%20kind%20neighbor%20lent%20us%20chainsaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetty-villa-survives-palisades-fire-lessons-for-homeowners-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrimmed%20the%20wild%20grasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20covered%20our%20hillside.%20We%20installed%20a%20gravel%20barrier%20around%20the%20house%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20stray%20ember%20landing%20and%20catching%20flame.%20We%20interviewed%20contractors%20for%20more%20complex%20projects%2C%20like%20installing%20roofing%20and%20ledge%20flashing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20work%2C%20but%20it%20was%20rewarding.%20Before%20we%20knew%20it%2C%20we%20were%20only%20a%20few%20list%20items%20away%20from%20earning%20our%20certification%20and%20feeling%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22differnet%20colors%20and%20sizes%20of%20gravel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e5b83d5881a51c1e2111%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rocks%20that%20Moore%20and%20her%20husband%20chose%20for%20their%20gravel%20barrier%2C%20which%20added%20defensible%20space%20around%20their%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20afternoon%2C%20a%20small%20wildfire%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20neighborhood%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20neighbor%20told%20us%20that%20someone%20operating%20a%20weedwhacker%20had%20nicked%20a%20rock%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20sparks%20had%20started%20a%20brush%20fire.%20I%20watched