0view%20from%20Moore's%20backyard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20our%20friends%20at%20Wildfire%20Partners%20were%20so%20stringent%20about%20handing%20out%20certifications.%20Details%20that%20could%20appear%20insignificant%2C%20such%20as%20decking%20gaps%20or%20the%20type%20of%20mesh%20covering%20your%20vents%2C%20actually%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20There%20was%20also%20hope%E2%80%94but%20not%20a%20promise%E2%80%94that%20the%20mitigations%20would%20help%20keep%20homes%20like%20ours%20insured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d3b5546-1d43-42cb-bba6-741b45773f23%5C%22%3EInsurance%20trends%20made%20us%20question%20our%20purchase%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20insurance%20landscape%20began%20to%20change.%20We%20heard%20through%20the%20neighborhood%20grapevine%20that%20a%20neighbor's%20insurer%20had%20dropped%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20in%20another%20part%20of%20the%20state%20also%20lost%20her%20coverage.%20Finally%2C%20we%20read%20that%20State%20Farm%2C%20our%20insurer%2C%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fire-insurance-coverage-cancellation-no-payout-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20issue%20new%20home%20policies%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Could%20Colorado%20be%20next%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20occurred%20to%20us%20that%20our%20safety%20net%2C%20which%20we%20paid%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20annually%20to%20secure%2C%20might%20not%20be%20there%20for%20us%20when%20we%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20in%20colorado%20wilderness%20in%20winter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e707f748d8c055f66920%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore%20on%20a%20hike%20with%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20wondering%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20we%20lost%20everything.%20Would%20our%20insurer%20provide%20us%20enough%20to%20rebuild%20in%20place%3F%20Would%20we%20even%20want%20to%3F%20And%20in%20the%20absolute%20worst-case%20scenario%20possible%E2%80%94if%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%2C%20would%20a%20neighbor%20rescue%20our%20dog%20if%20we%20were%20unable%20to%20get%20to%20her%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20beers%2C%20the%20same%20neighbors%20who%20lent%20us%20yard%20tools%20recounted%20tales%20of%20their%20most%20recent%20evacuation.%20The%202020%20CalWood%20Fire%20had%20burned%20over%2010%2C000%20acres.%20On%20their%20wall%20hung%20a%20framed%20photo%20of%20the%20blaze%2C%20which%20had%20ripped%20through%20the%20foothills%20just%20across%20the%20canyon%20and%20leveled%2026%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20their%20casual%20attitude%2C%20but%20they%20revealed%20important%20truths.%20We%20cannot%20control%20nature%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20preventative%20checklists%20we%20complete.%20Also%2C%20we%20are%20far%20from%20experiencing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-change-impacts-to-last-millennia-ipcc-report-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworst%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20as%20our%20government%20takes%20steps%20to%20halt%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommitting%20to%20life%20in%20a%20wildland-urban%20interface%20would%20require%20acceptance%20and%20a%20come-what-may%20point%20of%20view%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20wildfires%2C%20which%20we%20weren't%20sure%20we%20were%20up%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2816fc2-9caa-44d9-a9ef-e1bf3b9886f7%5C%22%3EWe%20sold%20in%202024%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221005%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wild%20turkey%20in%20colorado%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e6f1f748d8c055f66919%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22753%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20wild%20turkey%20in%20Moore's%20yard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20life%20on%20the%20mountain%20was%20far%20from%20perfect%2C%20but%20it%20had%20become%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20forward%20to%20the%20wild%20irises%20and%20larkspurs%20blooming.%20We%20even%20felt%20fond%20of%20the%20wild%20band%20of%20turkeys%20that%20sometimes%20woke%20us%20up%20at%206%20in%20the%20morning.%20Could%20we%20really%20leave%20it%20all%20behind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20everything%2C%20we%20were%20not%20resting%20easily.%20No%20matter%20how%20much%20we%20enjoyed%20it%20in%20the%20present%2C%20we%20feared%20our%20dream%20home%20could%20not%20be%20insured%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-will-home-prices-fall-sellers-listings-inventory-mortgage-rates-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esold%20in%20the%20future%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20dealbreaker%20for%20our%20neighbors%2C%20who%20plan%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20lives%20in%20this%20special%20place%E2%80%94come%20what%20may.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20because%20they%20are%20in%20their%20forever%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20we%20were%20not%20in%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20trusty%20realtor%20listed%20our%20dream%20home%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20and%20by%20summer%2C%20it%20closed.%20Although%20we%20came%20out%20in%20the%20red%2C%20we%20exhaled%20a%20massive%20sigh%20of%20relief.%20A%20few%20days%20after%20closing%2C%20a%20wildfire%20broke%20out%20in%20South%20Boulder%2C%20and%20I%20told%20that%20familiar%20pang%20of%20fear%20to%20take%20a%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20risk%2C%20our%20former%20mountain%20home%20is%20a%20magical%20place%20to%20live.%20We%20just%20weren't%20those%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-dream-colorado-mountain-home-but-sold-soon-after-2